      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "<br/> The spring-like weather conditions will give rise to unfavourable bonding of the snowpack in some cases on very steep sunny slopes. As a consequence of highly fluctuating temperatures and solar radiation a treacherous avalanche situation will develop. These conditions will cause a weakening of the snowpack in gullies and bowls and behind abrupt changes in terrain. This applies in particular on steep south, southwest and west facing slopes above the tree line."
      },
